---
title: Shawarma-Spiced Meatball Pitas with Israeli Salad & Tzatziki
description: Pita pockets are sandwich superheroes. They’re light, fluffy, and hold pretty much anything you want in their roomy pockets—so if you’re going to make a pita sandwich, it better be fully loaded. This one does not disappoint: The whole wheat pitas are stuffed with earthy and fragrant shawarma-spiced meatballs, plus creamy tzatziki and a refreshing cucumber and tomato salad. Drizzle over a little hot sauce if you like things spicy, then dig into pita perfection!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/shawarma-spiced-meatball-pitas-8a015c20.jpg
